    "hardcoded_asan_001_msg" to "Lost 40,000 ₸, but learned a lesson for life.\n\nI read 3 books on investing. Got it:\nindex ETFs > hype projects.\n\nReady to start investing the right way?",
    "hardcoded_asan_002_msg" to "Debt closed! 🎉 15,000 ₸/month freed up.\n\nCapital: \${(200_000L - 120_000L).moneyFormat()}.\nExpenses decreased by 15,000/month.\n\nWhat to do with the freed up money?",
    "hardcoded_asan_003_msg" to "The pillow is created - 60,000 ₸ lie untouched.\n\nNews: the phone is broken. You need 35,000 ₸.\nThis is exactly what the pillow exists for.",
    "hardcoded_asan_004_msg" to "This is exactly how an airbag works! ✅\n\nI bought a phone without stress and without debt.\nNow I’m replenishing the cushion - 15,000/month until it reaches 90,000.",
    "hardcoded_asan_005_msg" to "I took an installment plan of 38,000 ₸ at 20% per annum.\nThe pillow is intact, but a new debt has appeared.\n\nStrategically, it’s debatable. This is exactly what the pillow was needed for.",
    "hardcoded_asan_006_msg" to "The boss agreed to 600,000 ₸! 🎉\n\nShowed me the offer and it worked.\nStability + salary growth = ideal.\n\n+150k/month What to do with them?",
    "hardcoded_asan_007_msg" to "Stayed - a month later they announced a promotion!\nNow a middle worker with a salary of 550,000 ₸. 🎉\n\n+100k/month This is the first step to becoming a senior.",
    "hardcoded_asan_008_msg" to "I moved to a new place - 500k/month.\nA little less than a startup, but stable.\n\nThe downsizing experience has taught me that an airbag is not an option.\nNow the rule is 50/30/20.",
    "hardcoded_asan_009_msg" to "The first 50,000 ₸ in ETFs have been purchased! 📈\nTicker: KASE_IDX on KASE through Halyk Invest.\n\nA notification arrived a month later: +0.8% → +400 ₸.\nNot much, but compound interest does its job.\n\nNext - recruit a position regularly?",
    "hardcoded_asan_010_msg" to "The bank approved the mortgage on 7-20-25.\nApartment 18,000,000 ₸. Contribution 20% = 3,600,000 ₸.\nMortgage 14,400,000 ₸ at 7.5% for 20 years.\nPayment: ~115,000 ₸/month.\n\nNow I rent for 130,000/month - the mortgage payment is comparable.\nSavings: {capital}. To make a contribution you need 3,600,000.\nParents are ready to help get the rest.",
    "hardcoded_asan_011_msg" to "Income 900k/month. Expenses 200k. I invest 400k/month.\n\nThe portfolio is growing. Passive income through ETFs + dividends -\nalready 45,000 ₸/month.\n\nBefore passive income = expenses (~4-5 years at the current rate).\nBut the path is clear. You're on the right track!",
    "hardcoded_asan_012_msg" to "Life goes on as usual.\nYou work, you procrastinate, and sometimes you treat yourself.\n\nWhat's in focus this month?",
    "hardcoded_asan_013_msg" to "Learned new technology. Wrote an article on Medium.\n150 likes, 2 recruiters wrote in a personal message.\n\nOne is offering a Senior position right now.",
    "hardcoded_asan_014_msg" to "⚠️ DEBT CRISIS!\n\nThe debt exceeded 1,000,000 ₸.\nThe bank is calling. Collectors are sending letters.\nMaximum stress. Urgent measures are needed.",
    "hardcoded_asan_015_msg" to "😰 Paycheck to Paycheck Trap\n\nThere have been no savings for 6 months now.\nEvery month is zero.\n\nSomething needs to change.",
    "hardcoded_asan_016_msg" to "🎁 Unexpectedly: annual bonus!\n\nThe company showed record profits.\nYou were paid 200,000 ₸ on top.\n\nWhere to send?",
    "hardcoded_asan_017_msg" to "🏠 I saved up for the down payment!\n\nThere are already 2,800,000 ₸ in the account.\nThe bank pre-approved the mortgage on 7-20-25.\n\nWorth considering?",
    "hardcoded_asan_018_msg" to "😮‍💨 Burnout is on the horizon.\n\nThe stress is very high. Bad sleep.\nProductivity is falling.\n\nNeed to slow down.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_001_msg" to "There is no computer. There are no more part-time jobs as a programmer.\nYou saved your father, but abandoned your career.\nNow only physical labor.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_002_msg" to "📈 Prices in the store have increased by 40% in a month!\nBread: 5 ₸ → 7 ₸\nMilk: 12 ₸ → 17 ₸\n\nYour salary is only enough for food.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_003_msg" to "🏪 A friend suggests opening a stall with Chinese goods.\nInvestment: 200,000 ₸.\nIncome: up to 50,000 ₸/month.\n\nNeed a partner. Are you in?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_004_msg" to "🎉 The stall is open!\nThe first buyers arrived.\n\nBut the tax authorities are already interested...",
