    "hardcoded_aidar90s_010_msg" to "🎯 1999. You've been through everything.\n\nCapital: {capital}\nIncome: {income}/month\nKnowledge: {knowledge}/100\n\nWhat's next? Emigrate or stay to build a business?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_011_msg" to "🏆 FINANCIAL INDEPENDENCE (90s Style)\n\nAidar was able to catch the wave. \nCapital: {capital} (or \$10,000).\nYou opened your own store or went to Moscow.\n\nParents are saved. The 90s are over.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_012_msg" to "🏢 BUSINESS EMPIRE\n\nYour stall has grown into a chain of stores.\nYou are one of those who built a new Kazakhstan.\n\nBut how much health did it cost?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_013_msg" to "✈️EMIGRATION\n\nYou left in search of a better life.\nIn Germany/Russia you started from scratch.\n\nBut the children will speak German/Russian.\nThe homeland is a thing of the past.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_014_msg" to "💔 CRASH.\n\nInflation ate up the remainder. \nParents are in debt. \nYou were left without housing and funds.\n\nThe 90s do not forgive mistakes.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_015_msg" to "😐 FROM SALARY TO SALARY\n\nYou survived. But no more.\nThe 90s are over, and you are still counting every tenge.\n\nLife goes on...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_016_msg" to "A month has passed. Light is provided according to schedule.\nPrices in the store increased by 10%.\n\nWhat's your priority?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_017_msg" to "💼 Offered a job in a new company.\nSalary: 25,000 ₸/month (vs current 15,000).\n\nBut the company is dubious - they can close in a month.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_018_msg" to "🏥 Health is failing.\nStress and poor nutrition take their toll.\n\nTreatment: 20,000 ₸. Or endure?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_019_msg" to "🤝 A friend offers to invest in a common business.\nYou need 50,000 ₸. They promise 30% per annum.\n\nDo you trust him?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_020_msg" to "🌑 On the black market they offer dollars at a rate lower than the official one.\nYou can buy 20% cheaper.\n\nBut there is a risk of running into fakes or the police.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_021_msg" to "🎉 A relative of that one (wedding).\nYou need to donate at least 5,000 ₸.\n\nBut you're tight on money right now...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_022_msg" to "💡 Utility bills have arrived.\nLight, water, heating: 8,000 ₸.\n\nLights are turned off for non-payment...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_023_msg" to "🎓 Accounting/law courses have opened.\nCost: 30,000 ₸.\nDuration: 3 months.\n\nThis could open up new opportunities.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_024_msg" to "🚗 They sell the old “nine” for 150,000 ₸.\nThe car is needed for business/taxi.\n\nBut these are all your savings...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_025_msg" to "🏠 The owner of the apartment increases the rent by 5,000 ₸/month.\nOr look for new housing.\n\nMoving costs 10,000 ₸ and a lot of nerves.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_026_msg" to "❄️ Winter is coming. You need to stock up on coal/wood.\nCost: 15,000 ₸.\n\nYou can't survive the Almaty winter without heating.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_027_msg" to "📋 The tax office came with an inspection.\nWe found violations worth ₸50,000.\n\nPay or “negotiate”?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_028_msg" to "🎰 Won 10,000 ₸ in the lottery!\nNot rich, but nice.\n\nWhat will you do with your winnings?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_029_msg" to "👋 An old friend from Russia has returned.\nHe brought money and offered to start a joint business.\n\nDo you trust him after all these years?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_030_msg" to "👶You have a baby!\nCongratulations! 🎉\n\nBut expenses will increase by 10,000 ₸/month...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_031_msg" to "🚨 You were robbed!\n20,000 ₸ was stolen from my pocket.\n\nThe police won't help - they have enough problems of their own.",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_032_msg" to "💱 The dollar exchange rate has risen sharply!\nThose who bought earlier are in the black.\n\nBuy now or wait for the fall?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_033_msg" to "😡 Business partner disappeared with money!\nYour share: 50,000 ₸.\n\nSearch for it or accept the loss?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_034_msg" to "🏛️ The state has allocated subsidies for small businesses.\nYou can get 100,000 ₸ at 5% per annum.\n\nBut paperwork will take 2 months...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_035_msg" to "🚑 Urgent hospitalization of a relative.\nNeed 100,000 ₸ immediately.\n\nThese are all your savings...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_036_msg" to "🎄 New Year's bonus awarded: 30,000 ₸!\nWindfall.\n\nWhat will you do?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_037_msg" to "🏠 1-room apartment for sale for 2,000,000 ₸.\nYou can take it in installments: 500k immediately + 50k/month.\n\nThis is your chance to get a home!",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_038_msg" to "🗳️ There are political changes in the country.\nNew laws for business.\n\nAdapt or fade into the shadows?",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_039_msg" to "🎓 The child has grown up. Need a school.\nPrivate: 50,000 ₸/month. State: free.\n\nBut in the state there is no future for the school...",
    "hardcoded_aidar90s_040_msg" to "👴 Retirement in the 90s is a myth.\nBut you need to save for old age now.\n\nSave 10% of your income?",
